  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate the advantages of using AlignRT, a commercially available, FDA
      approved camera-based imaging system for proton therapy patients prior to and during their
      radiation treatment delivery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    Slow enrollment, feasibility issues
  </why_stopped>
